  "detailed_description": "Olgob The Bold is a <strong>Metroidvania Soulslike</strong> by a <strong>solo dev</strong>.<br><br>The story of an orc from a small tribe in the Greenskin Barrens. From a <strong>blue-collar, working-class family</strong>, hunting down <strong>billionaire Bear Lords</strong> who have taken control of the world by <strong>exploiting</strong> the labour of <strong>poor orcs</strong>. <br><br>Ruling with cruel <strong>taxes up to 75%</strong> for small business owners. And letting their bear friends register companies in <strong>tax havens</strong> in the Forgotten Lands. Olgob is the <strong>Strong Orc Leader</strong> they need to come and fix all their problems. <br><br>Play and help Olgob give power back to the people by <strong>overthrowing the government</strong> of the oppressive Bear Lords. <br><br>With over 500 lines of unique dialogue spoken in complete gibberish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/1bae76bf4321c7f3f04f971277818467.poster.avif?t=1681290080\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/1bae76bf4321c7f3f04f971277818467.webm?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/1bae76bf4321c7f3f04f971277818467.mp4?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join Olgob on his journey through the Mutating Castle to collect <strong>20 bear asses</strong> for a stranger in the woods... <br><br>That is it. This is your quest. The only quest you have in this game. Just the one. <strong>Collect 20 bear asses</strong>. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/b085d4b0f46d9f83702092a0441a19e2.poster.avif?t=1681290080\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/b085d4b0f46d9f83702092a0441a19e2.webm?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/b085d4b0f46d9f83702092a0441a19e2.mp4?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mutating Castle</h2><br>Players will traverse the Mutating Castle with <strong>interconnected areas</strong>, and changing pathways. Your world will change as you progress through the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/3d58ed0154850d65ee88f5dacc6f39e0.poster.avif?t=1681290080\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/3d58ed0154850d65ee88f5dacc6f39e0.webm?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/3d58ed0154850d65ee88f5dacc6f39e0.mp4?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story and Lore Rich World</h2><br>Discover the origin and story of the Bear Lords and their ascension as you piece together the secrets of the Mutating Castle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/d6572b21ffff3008deb22141e890449e.poster.avif?t=1681290080\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/d6572b21ffff3008deb22141e890449e.webm?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/d6572b21ffff3008deb22141e890449e.mp4?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slow Deliberate Combat</h2><br>Nothing is claimed easily. You will scratch and claw to victory every step of the way. You may say it is... just like <strong>Dark Souls</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/f373b71d1e5095d7fc3a7d253908afb8.poster.avif?t=1681290080\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/f373b71d1e5095d7fc3a7d253908afb8.webm?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/f373b71d1e5095d7fc3a7d253908afb8.mp4?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Colorful Cast of NPCs</h2><br>This game is all about the <strong>power of friendship</strong>. if you cannot do something alone, there is always someone who you can passively talk to and they will do nothing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/db1a1231110c43e85dd3b0c60663949e.poster.avif?t=1681290080\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/db1a1231110c43e85dd3b0c60663949e.webm?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971260/extras/db1a1231110c43e85dd3b0c60663949e.mp4?t=1681290080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>I plan on releasing free <strong>DLCs</strong> depending on how well this does.<br>You can contact me at <a href=\"mailto:crabjuicegaming@gmail.com\">crabjuicegaming@gmail.com</a> regarding any issues you may encounter in the game.",
